<title>Cuántos ves: 1, 2, 3</title>

<statement>
  <p>
    <line>¿Cuántos ves?</line>
    <line>¿Cómo lo sabes?, ¿qué ves?</line>
  </p>
  <p>
    <image source="svg-source/tikz-file-136322">
      <shortdescription>un punto</shortdescription>
    </image>
  </p>
  <p>
    <image source="svg-source/tikz-file-136323">
      <shortdescription>dos puntos</shortdescription>
    </image>
  </p>
  <p>
    <image source="svg-source/tikz-file-136324">
    <shortdescription>tres puntos</shortdescription>
    </image>
  </p>
</statement>

<solution>
  <p>[++++++++++++]</p>
  <p>Sample responses:</p>
  <ul>
    <li>1: There is only 1 dot.</li>
    <li>2: I just see 2. There is 1 more dot.</li>
    <li>3: There are 2 and 1. I see 3 dots.</li>
  </ul>
</solution>


